verses.roman:
govinda bale,--'rāghavera jhāli mātra āche'
prabhu kahe,--'āji rahu, tāhā dekhimu pāche'

synonyms: govinda bale—Govinda replied; rāghavera jhāli—the bags given by Rāghava; mātra—only; āche—there is; prabhu kahe—Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu said; āji—today; rahu—let remain; tāhā—that; dekhimu—I shall see; pāche—later.
translation: Govinda replied, "Now there are only the bags of Rāghava." The Lord said, "Let them remain today. I shall see them later."
